  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of Seladelpar in Subjects With Hepatic Impairment and Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open Label, Non-Randomized Study to Evaluate the Pharmacokinetics, Safety, and Tolerability of Oral Seladelpar in Subjects With Varying Degrees of Hepatic Impairment and Healthy Matched Control Subjects With Normal Hepatic Function</official_title>
