  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 1 open label study is being conducted to directly characterize the pharmacokinetic
      (PK) profiles of seladelpar following administration of a single oral dose in subjects with
      varying degrees of hepatic impairment (HI) compared to healthy matched control subjects with
      normal hepatic function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
